1 Enrolled, An Act,
2
3
4 Relating to the Alabama Space Authority; to amend
5 Sections 41-23-170, 41-23-171, 41-23-173, and 41-23-174, Code
6 of Alabama 1975, to rename the authority the Alabama Aerospace
7 and Defense Authority; to increase the membership of the
8 authority; and to further provide for the duties and powers of
9 the authority.
10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
11 Section 1. Sections 41-23-170, 41-23-171, 41-23-173,
12 and 41-23-174 of the Code of Alabama 1975, are amended to read
13 as follows:
14 "§41-23-170
15 There is hereby established the Alabama Space
16 Authority. Commencing on October 1, 2026, the name of the
17 Alabama Space Authority shall be the Alabama Aerospace and
18 Defense Authority, and all rights, duties, property, real or
19 personal, and all other effects existing in the name of the
20 Alabama Space Authority, or in any other name by which the
21 authority has been known, shall continue in the name of the
22 Alabama Aerospace and Defense Authority. Any existing or
23 future reference to the Alabama Space Authority, or any other
24 name by which the authority has been known, in any existing
25 law, contract, or other instrument, shall constitute a
26 reference to the Alabama Aerospace and Defense Authority."
